## Protected Routes

Routes are protected using a `ProtectedRoute` wrapper:

```typescript
<Route
  path="/dashboard"
  element={
    <ProtectedRoute>
      <DashboardPage />
    </ProtectedRoute>
  }
/>
```

Unauthenticated users are redirected to `/login`.

